Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(班導在制服按摩店工作)\N(指名之後竟然和我做了)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,(放學後)\N馬上就要畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒找到工作的我\N終日奔波在找工作的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一直支持著我的班導\N深田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的找到工作之前\N我都會一直支援你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿真的嗎  老師真的好溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-打起精神  繼績努力\N-我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿-挺直腰板  -我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-非常感謝\N-有自信最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-我會努力的\N-重要的是想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿是的  想法對吧  抱歉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-讓你這樣陪著我\N-沒事  我也很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好像一直都很無精打採的\N-對了  還要準備考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿-是嗎  -是的  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿ 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我從以前開始就一直都\N很喜歡這樣的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿(某天  在家看電腦的時候)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿還說要找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿作業都根本做不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,必須要有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿糟糕  搜索了女子高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿還有這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿-泡泡浴按摩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿也太可愛了阿伯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-太像深田老師了吧\N-泡泡浴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿泡泡浴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨  泡泡浴\N我是深田繪美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這個衣服可愛嗎\N好好看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我非常喜歡教別人學習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但認識我的人可能不知道\N我在做這麼色情的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我也很喜歡教別人\N做色情的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,(方案1  制服繪美)\N(自我介紹自慰)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,泡泡浴樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的肉棒也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿像這樣很硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿對I嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿摸一摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿用繪美的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿什麼叫舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿胸部裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿繪美的這裡  硬了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿肉棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿頂端
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我的乳頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿還有這邊的乳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的肉棒和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿繪美的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿一起摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿繪美很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿要夾在胸部裡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿越來越
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿還想要更舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿直接把肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿放進這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿就會更舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿在繪美的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿的裡面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿被繪美的胸部包裏著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的肉棒變得非常硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿繪美興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿要好好享受一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿越來越硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿這個硬硬的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太硬了  可能可以直接插進\N繪美的小穴裡面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿插進來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿要插進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿在在這裡摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要把你的肉棒插進繪美的\N裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿要插進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿那麼  慢慢插進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿別急
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿要進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿龜頭進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿慢慢被肉棒插進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿龜頭被繪美的裡面夾住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿只有龜頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿在抽插了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿肉棒的龜頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿肯定很有感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿要插到最裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿插到最裡面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿會更舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿插進來好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿要進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,插到最裡面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿插到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿最裡面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的肉棒  很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的硬肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我的裡面被抽插了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿太硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我的裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿被抽插得好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我的小穴舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿又溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿又濕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿還很緊對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿肉棒好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在我的小穴裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿抽插
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿繼續用肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿抽插我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好厲害  小穴裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿小穴裡面濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好厲害  舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我的濕透的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好舒服  太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿裡面好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿再次光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿這個也太棒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我也去去泡泡浴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿這個啊  我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿喂你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我想預約
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好的  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,(方案2  果然是深田老師)\N(極品淫蕩椅子方案)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,泡泡浴樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你好  歡迎光臨  失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿-謝謝你光臨  -是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你是深田老師對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是高田嗎  為什麼啊\N-在網上找到了所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-找到了  是嗎\N-沒想到真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:18:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿太開心了  你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿-太可愛了 -可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一起開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿-可以嗎  -脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-太害羞了\N一畢竟第一次對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-這種店是第一次  -是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-好厲害的衣服\N-厲青嗎  興奮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-這個也脫掉吧\N-太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我也第一次看  給你圍上毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿-來  -好的  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿-過來這邊  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿-坐這裡吧  -這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿我是這次的擔當  深田繪美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿老師的這個樣子有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-非常適合你哦\N-真的嗎  老帥的這種衣服
